(1) InnerWidth
---------------
==> The innerWidth property returns the width of a window's content area.


EX
-----

	// Get Window Document Inner Width
	window.innerWidth
	
	// Get Window Document Inner Width
	innerWidth
	
	

(2) InnerHeight
---------------
==> The innerHeight property returns the height of a window's content area.


EX
------

	// Get Window Document Inner Height
	window.innerHeight
	
	// Get Window Document Inner Height
	innerHeight
